Package com.nitrous.gwt.earth.client.demo

Class Summary
BalloonListenerDemo An extended version of the "closing ballons" demo that shows how to use a Balloon Listener.
ClosingBalloonsDemo A GWT implementation of the closing balloons demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/?exp=earth#closing_balloons
ExecuteBatchDemo This demo illustrates the performance difference that can be obtained by taking advantage of batch execution.
FetchBadKmlDemo A GWT implementation of the demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/#fetch_bad_kml
FetchGoodKmlDemo A GWT implementation of the demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/#fetch_good_kml
FrameEndDemo A GWT implementation of the frame end demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/?exp=earth#smooth_animation_with_frameend
HelloWorldDemo This demo shows how to get the map displayed in your GWT application
KmlExtendedDataDemo A demo that shows how to access ExtendedData in the Kml Document Based upon the original JavaScript demo here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/#extended_data_in_balloons
MouseListenerDemo An demo that shows how to use a Mouse Listener to monitor mouse interaction with Google Earth
MovingPlacemarkDemo This sample plots a location on the map and then moves that placemark once every second
NetworkLinkDemo A demo that shows how to create network links.
ParseKmlDemo This demo shows how to parse KML.
PlacemarkStyleMapDemo A GWT implementation of the "Styling Placemarks using Style Maps" demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/#styling_placemarks_using_style_maps
ViewChangeDemo A GWT implementation of the view change demo found here: http://code.google.com/apis/ajax/playground/?exp=earth#viewchange_event_%28and_viewchangebegin,_viewchangeend%29
